y-five, he still thinks, every so often, that under the right circumstances he could be the baddest motherfucker in the world. If I moved to a martial-arts monastery in China and studied real hard for ten years. If my family was wiped out by Colombian drug dealers and I swore myself to revenge. If I got a fatal disease, had one year to live, and devoted it to wiping out street crime. If I just dropped out and devoted my life to being bad.', 2217, 0), (8450, 'There are moments, Jeeves, when one asks oneself, ''Do trousers matter?''""The mood will pass, sir.', 273, 0);
