ers will vaporize when sliced with a celestial bronze sword. This change is completely normal, and will happen to you right now if you don''t BACK OFF!"To my surprise, it worked. The monsters backed off, but there was at least twenty of them. My fear factor wasn''t going to last that long.I jumped out of the cart, yelled, "CLASS DISMISSED!" and ran for the exit.', 80, 0), (8545, 'I have never voted in my life... I have always known and understood that the idiots are in a majority so it''s certain they will win.', 2227, 0), (8546, 'Five syllables," Apollo said, counting them on his fingers. "That would be real bad.', 80, 0), (8547, 'He''d changed since the last summer. Instead of Bermuda shorts and a T-shirt, he wore a button-down shirt, khaki pants, and leather loafers. His sandy hair, which used to be so unruly, was now clipped short. He look like an evil male model, showing off what the fashionable college-age villain was wearing to Harvard this year.', 80, 0), (8548, 'Well, that''s an evil smile...', 285, 0), (8549, 'An appeaser is one who feeds a crocodile, hoping it will eat him last.', 1150, 0), (8550, 'Siblings that say they never fight are most definitely hiding something', 59, 0);
