am taped to it. My GTO could dust the fucker in fourth gear from a dead stop."When there was an odd sound from behind, John looked back. So did the three Brothers. "What." Xhex bristled and crossed her arms over her chest. "I can laugh, you know. And that''s . . . pretty damn funny." Rhage beamed. "I knew I liked you.', 108, 0), (9309, 'A word to the wise is infuriating. ', 126, 0), (9310, 'When I was in school the teachers told me practice makes perfect', 2316, 0), (9311, 'If I was made of cake I''d eat myself before somebody else could.', 1308, 0), (9312, 'Three be the things I shall never attain: Envy, content, and sufficient champagne.', 201, 0), (9313, 'Yes, vanity is a weakness indeed. But pride - where there is a real superiority of mind, pride will be always under good regulation.', 24, 0), (9314, 'Here''s an easy way to figure out if you''re in a cult: If you''re wondering whether you''re in a cult, the answer is yes.', 1450, 0), (9315, 'Enormous? Did you just call me FAT? I am not fat. - Jace', 39, 0), (9316, 'I never met a man that I didn''t like.', 1122, 0), (9317, 'There is only one cure for grey hair. It was invented by a Frenchman. It is called the guillotine.', 273, 0), (9318, 'Two things that matter to me. Emotional resonance and rocket launchers.', 1099, 0), (9319, 'I’m forever near a stereo saying, ‘What the fuck is this garbage?’ And the answer is always the Red Hot Chili Peppers.', 2317, 0), (9320, 'I''ve seen more intelligence in the crotch lice of harem whores.', 612, 0), (9321, 'Um," Doc said in a mild voice, "medically speaking, I''m not sure that was the most helpful thing for his condition.""But I feel better," Jared answered, sullen.Doc smiled the tiniest smile. "Well, maybe a few more minutes of unconsciousness won''t kill him.', 50, 0), (9322, 'I, myself, have killed six people. All random, all undetected, no way to trace them to me. And, let me tell you, there''s nothin'' like it. It''s a great feeling. Yeah, I know, you''re thinking. 