h my hands on my hips, only slightly intimidated to find Kaleb almost eye level with me when he was seated and I was standing."First of all, no one is the boss of me but me. Secondly, if you ever reference my ''chain'' again, I will kick your ass." I jabbed him hard in the chest with my finger. Possibly breaking it. "And thirdly, don''t call me Shorty."Kaleb sat silently for a second, his eyes wide as he looked at Michael. "Where did you get her? Can you get me one?"I blew out a loud, frustrated sigh and dropped down beside Michael, who didn''t even try to hide his smile. "You should probably apologize to Emerson.""I am sorry." Kaleb grinned at me. "Sorry I didn''t meet you first.', 2341, 0), (9461, 'Rincewind could scream for mercy in nineteen languages, and just scream in another forty-four.', 195, 0), (9462, 'You okay?""Fine.""Your heart''s beating really fast.""Gee, thanks. That''s very comforting that you can hear it."He smiled, and it was the old Michael, the one she''d first met before all the vamp stuff."Yeah, I know it is. Sorry. Just stay behind me if there''s trouble.""You sound like Shane.""Well, he did say he''d kill me if I got you hurt. I''m just looking after my own neck.""Liar.', 614, 0), (9463, 'I am human and I need to be loved,just like everybody else does.', 1259, 0), (9464, 'She can go with us to the lab and keep Myrnin pinned down while we pull the plug, if he''s not... you know, better.""Define BETTER with that guy.""Not all fangs and raaaaar.', 614, 0), (9465, 'If your kid needs a role model and you ain''t it, you''re both fucked.', 1003, 0), (9466, 'How ghastly for her, people actually thinking, with their brains, and right next door. Oh, the travesty of it all.', 2342, 0), (9467, 'Because sometimes you just have to dance like a madman in the Self-Help section of your local bookstore.', 251, 0), (9468, 'Mirrors should think longer before they reflect.', 2343, 0), (9469, 'Buttercup''s mother whirled on him. ''Did you forget to pay your taxes